author: chris-dollin
msg: Tidied up the code for ModelCom::getRDFNode which now calls
asRDFNode (and hence enjoys the same caching behaviour).
Modified ModelTestBase::rdfNode to use asRDFNode, which I
think got added later: minor but useful tidying.
(Thanks to Andy for asking the question that provoked this)

author: chris-dollin
msg: Revised the GraphMemFaster codebase so that removing
a triple via an iterator::remove operation removed the
Bunch from its Map if it had become empty.

author: chris-dollin
msg: Refined BunchMap so that it can only contain TripleBunch's.
Fixed some dependencies. Note that this will slow GraphMem
down slightly - since it relies on getting at a now-embedded
Set object - but in any case GraphMem is obsolete.
